self.setUpClass()
nqubits = 7
p = ql.Program('AllXY', platf, nqubits)
k = ql.Kernel('AllXY_q0', platf, nqubits)
q = 0
pulse_combinations = [['I', 'I'], ['rx180', 'rx180'], ['ry180', 'ry180'], [
    'rx180', 'ry180'], ['ry180', 'rx180'], ['rx90', 'I'], ['ry90', 'I'], [
    'rx90', 'ry90'], ['ry90', 'rx90'], ['rx90', 'ry180'], ['ry90', 'rx180'],
    ['rx180', 'ry90'], ['ry180', 'rx90'], ['rx90', 'rx180'], ['rx180',
    'rx90'], ['ry90', 'ry180'], ['ry180', 'ry90'], ['rx180', 'I'], ['ry180',
    'I'], ['rx90', 'rx90'], ['ry90', 'ry90']]
nr_sweep_pts = len(pulse_combinations)
for pulse_comb in pulse_combinations:
    k.prepz(q)
    k.gate(pulse_comb[0], [q])
    k.gate(pulse_comb[1], [q])
    k.measure(q)
p.add_kernel(k)
p.set_sweep_points([nr_sweep_pts])
p.compile()
